Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the control flow of the Bee Green application:

```plantuml
@startuml JessNah_BeeGreen

actor User
participant "Chrome Extension" as Extension
participant "Client Website" as Client
participant "LoopBack 4 Server" as Server
database "IBM Cloudant DB" as DB

User -> Extension: Open e-commerce site
activate Extension

Extension -> Extension: Inject content script
Extension -> Server: Request product data
activate Server
Server -> DB: Query product information
DB --> Server: Return product data
Server --> Extension: Send product data
deactivate Server

Extension -> Extension: Calculate sustainability score
Extension -> Extension: Display score and alternatives

User -> Extension: Contribute product review
activate Extension
Extension -> Server: Send review data
activate Server
Server -> DB: Store review
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Extension: Confirm submission
deactivate Server
deactivate Extension

User -> Client: Access dashboard
activate Client
Client -> Server: Request user data
activate Server
Server -> DB: Query user information
DB --> Server: Return user data
Server --> Client: Send user data
deactivate Server

Client -> Client: Display dashboard

User -> Client: Contribute to public database
activate Client
Client -> Server: Send contribution data
activate Server
Server -> DB: Store contribution
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Client: Confirm submission
deactivate Server
deactivate Client

@enduml
```